21 yd1a ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. </div><div class="t mb31 x4b he yc44 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">678 (1950 ed., p. 667). </div><div class="t m1bd x4b he y8ad ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m1593 x54 he y1278 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How fully will the mystery of </div><div class="t m858 xbc he y1fe7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">redemption and the &quot;wisdom of God&quot; </div><div class="t m360 xbc he y8d0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be the object </div><div class="t m57a xc6 h2d y8d0 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of </div><div class="t m885 xef he ya67 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our study? Eph. 3: </div><div class="t m6dd x6e he y538 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9-11. </div><div class="t m639 x86 he y15a7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—&quot;All the treasures of the universe &apos; </div><div class="t m271 xbc he y580 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will be open to the study of God&apos;s children. </div><div class="t m8bb x6e he ya44 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.With unutterable delight we shall enter </div><div class="t mdb xbc he y8ff ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">into the joy and the wisdom of unfallen </div><div class="t md30 xbc he y820 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beings. We shall share the treasures gained </div><div class="t m417 xbc he y661 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through ages upon ages spent in contem-</div><div class="t m68f x21 he y9a1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plation of God&apos;s handiwork. And the years </div><div class="t m128 xbc he y39f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of eternity, as they roll, will continue to </div><div class="t md4 xbc he y6d0 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bring more glorious revelations. &apos;Exceed-</div><div class="t m3c7 xbc he y721 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing abundantly above all that we ask or </div><div class="t m3f5 x21 he y46d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">think&apos; will be, forever and forever, the im-</div><div class="t m64d x21 he y15a8 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">partation of the gifts of </div><div class="t md02 xc8 h21 y15a8 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls